dered as</i></small> <code><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RGB_color_model\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:RGB color model\">RGB</a> 244 245 240</code></td><td><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pantone\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:Pantone\">Pantone</a> 11-0601</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"middle\">\n<td><span style=\"background-color:#CD212A;border:1px solid darkgray;\" title=\"#CD212A\">    </span> Scarlet Red</td>\n<td><small><i>rendered as</i></small> <code><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RGB_color_model\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:RGB color model\">RGB</a> 205 <span style=\"visibility:hidden\">0</span>33 <span style=\"visibility:hidden\">0</span>42</code></td><td><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pantone\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:Pantone\">Pantone</a>  18-1662</td></tr></tbody></table>", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "Artist": {"value": "See below.", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "Permission": {"value": "<table class=\"licensetpl\" style=\"display:none\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span class=\"licensetpl_short\">Public domain</span><span class=\"licensetpl_long\">Public domain</span><span class=\"licensetpl_link_req\">false</span><span class=\"licensetpl_attr_req\">false</span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; clear: both; margin: 0.5em auto; background-color: var(--background-color-progressive-subtle, #f7f8ff); color: var(--color-base, #202122); border: var(--border-subtle, 2px solid #8888aa); border-spacing: 8px; padding: 0px;\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"layouttemplate\" lang=\"en\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span title=\"Public domain\"><img alt=\"Public domain\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/62/PD-icon.svg/120px-PD-icon.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/62/PD-icon.svg/250px-PD-icon.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"196\" data-file-height=\"196\"></span></span>\n</t